In this confusing world of spirituality and religion, Gnosis can serve as a beacon of light which unites all perspectives into one cohesive whole. But even within gnosis, there are many different factions and contrasting teachings. Our mission is to fill in the gaps and provide resources for people to follow their own individual inner path while connecting with fellow truth seekers around the world.

Gnosis - hover definition
1. Knowledge acquired from direct inner experience
2. Teachings transmitted from a master's inner gnosis (e.g. Jesus, Buddha, Samael) especially syncretic, universal teachings

